Punjab
Nov 18, 2014
Rape
Description:
			A 30-year-old woman was allegedly raped by a friend of her father-in-law for over a year.

In her complaint lodged yesterday, the victim has alleged that one Amarjit Singh, a friend of her father-in-law had raped her and threatened her with consequences if she disclosed it to anyone, they said.

No arrest has been made so far, police said.

